      "text": "今度のイベントなんですが、ステージが狭いので\nフォーメーションをいつもと少し変えてみませんか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.294557666799999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "フォーメーション変更に合わせて新しい振り付けを\nこころと考えてみたので、後で感想を聞かせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5,
      "endTime": 14.7912700653,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
