      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "二人ともたくましくなったね\n自分から積極的に提案することも増えて、頼もしいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2666666667,
      "endTime": 38.746666495,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-ai004.m4a",
      "text": "リズノワが『Grab the BIG4』を\n勝ち抜いていた時に、こころと話したんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.9333333333,
      "endTime": 44.4567572911,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-ai005.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんと葵さんを追いかけるだけじゃいけない……\nこれからは私達がリズノワを背負って立つんだ、って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6666666667,
      "endTime": 52.5031747501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-ai006.m4a",
      "text": "見ていて下さい。莉央さんや葵さんのことも私達が\n背負うくらいの気持ちでこれからも頑張りますから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.7,
      "endTime": 60.3000001908,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、さっきから莉央さんが喋ってないんですけど\n愛ちゃんが生意気だから怒ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5,
      "endTime": 66.9344671249,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-ai007.m4a",
      "text": "生意気なことなんて言ってないよ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1333333333,
      "endTime": 69.79861157730001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.9666620891
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "別に怒ってないわよ。ただ、今は\n目の前のパンケーキを食べることに集中したいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.9666620891,
      "endTime": 76.9946894329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.2001317661
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio Kanzaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "一番美味しい時間……パンケーキのゴールデンタイムが\n終わる前に食べ切りたいから、私のことは気にしないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2001317661,
      "endTime": 84.67834059409999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.8837829273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせ場所にパンケーキの美味しい店を選んだのは\n失敗だったかもしれませんね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8837829273,
      "endTime": 90.8042591732,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.0171162606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-ai008.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせと言えば、リズノワの海外ツアー追加公演の\n打ち合わせもそろそろ始まりますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0171162606,
      "endTime": 97.8213114739,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.0171162606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "海外ツアーが好評だとは聞いてたけど\n追加公演までやることになるとはね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0171162606,
      "endTime": 103.944803238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 104.1504495939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "LizNoirの海外人気はうなぎ登りですから\nこのまま世界一のアイドルになっちゃいますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.1504495939,
      "endTime": 110.7144180617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.9171162606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだ！　追加公演に向けて新曲を作りませんか？\n新生リズノワにふさわしい神曲を爆誕させるんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.9171162606,
      "endTime": 119.5644177438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.7504495939
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai Komiyama",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-ai009.m4a",
      "text": "新曲をひっさげて追加公演に乗り込むんだね\nそれ、凄くいいアイデアだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.7504495939,
      "endTime": 125.8829891523,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.0837829273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "新曲か……。あのさ、もし制作することになったら\nその時は僕に曲作りを仕切らせてもらえないかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.0837829273,
      "endTime": 137.8957782428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.0837829273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro Akazaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
