      "text": "葵さんが自分からやりたがるなんてめずらしいですね\nいつもは面倒くさがってやろうとしないのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0837829273,
      "endTime": 145.0540500324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.2504445077
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi Igawa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2511_01_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "心外だな。僕は面倒くさがりな訳じゃない\n興味がわかないとやる気にならないだけだ",
